pageTitle: Energy Chair Aubertine Calls New Reactor in Oswego a Priority | New York State Senate
TableContextTimeStampBeforeTable: {11567=OSWEGO (June 10, 2009)—Continuing the work he was elected to do, state Sen. Darrel J. Aubertine today pledged his unwavering support to the Nuclear Regulatory Commission for a proposed fourth nuclear reactor in Oswego, calling it an economic stimulus for the region that requires no taxpayer funding.}
